cards.title: Volcanic ash plumes impact flight services; Air India cancels flights, inspects aircraft
cards.abstract: Flight operations faced disruptions on Tuesday due to volcanic ash from Ethiopia. Several international flights were cancelled and delayed. Air India cancelled 13 flights as aircraft underwent checks. The ash cloud is moving away from India. Authorities are monitoring the situation closely. Airlines were advised to avoid affected areas.
